<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَفُرُوضُهُ سِتَّةٌ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> غَسْلُ الوَجْهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- وَمِنْهُ فَمٌ وَأَنْفٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَغَسْلُ اليَدَيْنِ مَعَ المِرْفَقَيْنِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> وَمَسْحُ الرَّأْسِ كُلِّهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَمِنْهُ الأُذُنَانِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٤]</span> وَغَسْلُ الرِّجْلَيْنِ مَعَ الكَعْبَيْنِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٥]</span> وَتَرْتِيبٌ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٦]</span> وَمُوَالَاةٌ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَيَسْقُطَانِ مَعَ غُسْلٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- يَجُوزُ المَسْحُ عَلَى الخُفَّيْنِ وَنَحْوِهِمَا بِسَبْعَةِ شُرُوطٍ <span style="color:#008000">(١)</span>:<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> لُبْسُهُمَا بَعْدَ كَمَالِ طَهَارةٍ بِمَاءٍ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) وزاد في المنتهى (١/ ٦٣) شرطاً ثامناً: أن لا يكون واسعًا يرى منه بعض محل الفرض.</p> </div>